caption.title: Mice were i.v. injected with 2μg of a control- or Flt3-L- encoding plasmid and 24h later were infected or not with IAV.
caption.p: Four days later, the mean of fluorescent intensity (MFI) of CD135 expression on BM pre-DCs ( left panel) and the number of lung neutrophils ( right panel) were analyzed by flow cytometry. Means ± SEM of 6–12 mice are represented. **, p < 0.01; ***, p < 0.001.
